ence, not ownership.\n- Use previews and observed targets to choose turns.\n- In summaries, cite `session_key`, relevant `turn_key`s, target used, and record snippets only when needed.\n```\n\nI’d probably keep `IMPLEMENTATION-NOTES.md` too, but make the skill the operational artifact. The note is for maintainers; the skill is for agents.","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-21T03:22:45.029Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","phase":"final_answer"}}}